\[P\left(A_1 \cup A_2 \cup ... \cup A_n\right) = \sum_{i=1}^{n} P(A_i) - \sum_{i < j} P(A_i \cap A_j) + \sum_{i < j < k} P(A_i \cap A_j \cap A_k) - ... + (-1)^{n+1}P(A_1 \cap A_2 \cap ... \cap A_n)\]

